# Frontend React Standards

- Never write fake UI, mock data, or placeholders.
- If a React component needs a data pipeline, state the database schema and FastAPI requirement first.
- TypeScript in React files must have zero `any` types.
- Maintain zero lint errors.
- React components use `kebab-case.tsx`.
